  subject={"Unique places to visit in Europe"}
  keywords={"Europe travel, unique places Europe, globally distinctive travel, Europe map"}
  eyebrow={"Europe field guide"}
  dek={"A Europe list built for travelers who care about deep rarity first: geology, ecology, archaeology, sacred sites, difficult access and places that are hard to replace with a prettier version nearby."}
  criteriaText={"Trip estimates are per person from London via Heathrow (LHR). The origin follows the busiest-airport methodology for this region. The order is the ranking. Higher means rarer globally, more mind-expanding or harder to replace with a similar trip. Estimates assume economy flights where needed, midrange lodging, meals, local transfers, required fees and the shortest realistic visit."}
  tripOriginLabel={"From London"}
